I do not wish to displease you.

499
00:57:03,947 --> 00:57:06,916
I do not wish to displease you.

500
00:57:26,970 --> 00:57:29,939
Such reverence!

501
00:57:31,975 --> 00:57:33,840
Such an honour!

502
00:57:33,977 --> 00:57:36,844
Thank you, my dear gentlemen!

503
00:57:36,980 --> 00:57:39,949
Do not trouble yourselves.

504
00:57:41,985 --> 00:57:44,852
I'll do everything I can.

505
00:57:44,988 --> 00:57:47,855
But I can't do anything more.

506
00:57:47,991 --> 00:57:50,858
Here comes my niece.

507
00:57:50,994 --> 00:57:53,963
I must present myself.

508
00:57:55,999 --> 00:57:57,967
Taddeo...

509
00:58:00,003 --> 00:58:02,904
It would have been better...

510
00:58:05,942 --> 00:58:08,911
...if you had sunk...

511
00:58:10,947 --> 00:58:15,814
...to the bottom of the sea.

512
00:58:15,950 --> 00:58:17,818
- Viva!
- Thank you!

513
00:58:17,954 --> 00:58:20,923
- Viva!
- Such an honour!

514
